title: FANTOM Update: Raise $USDC, $DAI, $BTC, $ETH Collateral Cap
body:
Intro: This is a vote to update the collateral cap on FANTOM C.R.E.A.M. market for the following assets: USDC, DAI, BTC, ETH.

Proposal: Listing Committee

Rational: Update and improve FANTOM market.

For:
Raise Collateral Cap: 
Asset - $amt; token amt
 
USDC - $5,000,000; 5,000,000
DAI - $5,000,000; 5,000,000
BTC - $3,000,000; 65
ETH - $750,000; 234

Against:
Do not make any changes to FANTOM market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
